description: Gets a list of the pipeline executions.

parameters.name: PipelineName
parameters.description: The name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the pipeline.

nested_items.name: PipelineExecutionSummaries
nested_items.description: Contains a sorted list of pipeline execution summary objects matching the specified filters. Each run summary includes the Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the pipeline execution, the run date, and the status. This list can be empty.

nested_items.name: PipelineExecutionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the pipeline execution.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The start time of the pipeline execution.

nested_items.name: PipelineExecutionStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the pipeline execution.

nested_items.name: PipelineExecutionDescription
nested_items.description: The description of the pipeline execution.

nested_items.name: PipelineExecutionDisplayName
nested_items.description: The display name of the pipeline execution.

nested_items.name: PipelineExecutionFailureReason
nested_items.description: A message generated by SageMaker Pipelines describing why the pipeline execution failed.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the result of the previous ListPipelineExecutions request was truncated, the response includes a NextToken. To retrieve the next set of pipeline executions, use the token in the next request.
